[3]  Create a restaurant website using HTML and CSS that focuses on creating an attractive
and well-structured layout. It helps practice menu design, image alignment, color
themes, and responsive styling for a visually appealing user experience.
● Build a restaurant webpage to showcase strong HTML and CSS skills with a more
complex and detailed layout.
● Use CSS Grid to align food items, drinks, prices, and images in a clean and
organized manner.
● Enhance visual appeal with suitable color combinations, font styles, image galleries,
and optional sliding images.

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Restaurant Website</title>

    <style>

        body
        {
            font-family: Arial;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        /* Header */

        .header
        {
            background-color: darkred;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Navigation */

        .navbar
        {
            background-color: black;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .navbar a
        {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        /* Banner Image */

        .banner img
        {
            width: 100%;
            height: 300px;
        }

        /* Menu Section */

        .menu
        {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .menu h2
        {
            text-align: center;
            color: darkred;
        }

        /* Grid Layout */

        .grid-container
        {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: auto auto auto;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .item
        {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .item img
        {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .price
        {
            color: green;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Footer */

        .footer
        {
            background-color: black;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Header -->

    <div class="header">
        <h1>Royal Restaurant</h1>
        <p>Delicious Food & Drinks</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation -->

    <div class="navbar">
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">Menu</a>
        <a href="#">Gallery</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Banner -->

    <div class="banner">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504674900247-0877df9cc836" alt="Restaurant Image">
    </div>

    <!-- Menu Section -->

    <div class="menu">

        <h2><u>Our Special Menu</u></h2>

        <div class="grid-container">

            <!-- Item 1 -->

            <div class="item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565299624946-b28f40a0ae38" alt="Pizza">

                <h3>Pizza</h3>

                <p>Tasty cheese pizza with fresh toppings.</p>

                <p class="price">₹250</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 2 -->

            <div class="item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550547660-d9450f859349" alt="Burger">

                <h3>Burger</h3>

                <p>Fresh burger with crispy fries.</p>

                <p class="price">₹180</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 3 -->

            <div class="item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1546069901-ba9599a7e63c" alt="Pasta">

                <h3>Pasta</h3>

                <p>Italian pasta with creamy sauce.</p>

                <p class="price">₹220</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 4 -->

            <div class="item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512621776951-a57141f2eefd" alt="Salad">

                <h3>Salad</h3>

                <p>Healthy vegetable salad.</p>

                <p class="price">₹150</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 5 -->

            <div class="item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1495474472287-4d71bcdd2085" alt="Coffee">

                <h3>Coffee</h3>

                <p>Hot coffee with rich flavor.</p>

                <p class="price">₹120</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 6 -->

            <div class="item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1547592180-85f173990554" alt="Ice Cream">

                <h3>Ice Cream</h3>

                <p>Cold and sweet dessert.</p>

                <p class="price">₹100</p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->

    <div class="footer">
        <p>© 2026 Royal Restaurant | All Rights Reserved</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
